sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Learner
    participant Phase1 as Phase 1: Foundation
    participant Phase2 as Phase 2: Cloud Basics
    participant Phase3 as Phase 3: IaC
    participant Phase4 as Phase 4: Contaainerization
    participant Phase5 as Phase 5: CI/CD
    participant Phase6 as Final: Observability

    Learner->>Phase1: Start DevOps Journey
    note right of Phase1: Focus:\n- Linux fundamentals\n- Bash scripting\n- Git (version control)\n\nNotes:\n- Most DevOps systems run on Linux\n- Strong foundation is mandatory\n- Duration: 1–2 months
    Phase1-->>Learner: Solid OS & Version Control Skills

    Learner->>Phase2: Learn Cloud Basics
    note right of Phase2: Cloud Providers:\n- AWS (recommended)\n- Azure\n- GCP\n- Oracle\n- Alibaba\n\nNotes:\n- Learn compute, storage, networking first\n- Focus on 5 core services only\n- Hands-on projects > certifications\n- Duration: 1–2 months
    Phase2-->>Learner: Cloud Infrastructure Understanding

    Learner->>Phase3: Infrastructure as Code
    note right of Phase3: Tools:\n- Terraform\n- Pulumi\n\nNotes:\n- Understand IaC concepts & purpose\n- Practice provisioning cloud infrastructure\n- Solve real infrastructure problems\n- Duration: ~1 month
    Phase3-->>Learner: Automated Infrastructure Provisioning

    Learner->>Phase4: Containerization
    note right of Phase4: Technologies:\n- Docker\n- Kubernetes (container orchestration)\n\nNotes:\n- Focus on core 20% features\n- Covers 80% of real use cases\n- Duration: 1–2 months
    Phase4-->>Learner: Scalable Containerized Applications

    Learner->>Phase5: Build CI/CD Pipelines
    note right of Phase5: Tools:\n- Jenkins\n- GitHub Actions\n- GitLab CI\n\nNotes:\n- Understand CI/CD concepts deeply\n- Pick ONE tool and master it\n- Build end-to-end pipelines\n- Deploy to containerized systems\n- Duration: 1–2 months
    Phase5-->>Learner: Automated Build & Deployment

    Learner->>Phase6: Learn Observability
    note right of Phase6: Tools:\n- Prometheus\n- Grafana\n\nNotes:\n- Monitoring & metrics basics\n- Essential for production systems\n- Duration: ~1 month
    Phase6-->>Learner: Production-Ready DevOps Engineer

    note over Learner: Key Advice:\n- Avoid learning tools in isolation\n- Combine tools into real projects\n- Avoid shallow tutorials\n- Practice continuously\n- Identify and close knowledge gaps
